posts.author: YodaBannon
posts.title: It has begun

posts.raw_content:
My Brother:  "Remember that first St. Patrick's day after Dad died?"

Me: "Yeah?"

My Brother: "You and Missy were screaming at each other at the kitchen table while Mom was plating up dinner, and Missy called you a fucking asshole. From the kitchen,  Mom beaned her in the forehead with a boiled potato."

A food fight ensued, and we laughed our asses off as boiled cabbage joined boiled potatoes in the air.   It was one of the best ten minutes of my life, and worth the hour plus clean it up.

Mom was laughing her ass off, as well.

The point being?  Life is short.  Enjoy it.  Live it..
